snippet: Top-seeded Simona Halep and second-seeded Garbiñe Muguruza lost in the second round of the Dubai Tennis Championships to leave the tournament in the United Arab Emirates without any of its eight seeded players....
lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Simona Halep and second-seeded Garbiñe Muguruza lost in the second round of the Dubai Tennis Championships to leave the tournament in the United Arab Emirates without any of its eight seeded players.
abstract: Top-seeded Simona Halep loses in second round of Dubai Tennis Championships, along with second-seeded Garbine Muguruza; other tennis scores noted.

headline.main: Top-Seeded Simona Halep Falls in Dubai
